These is the install file for the Ask extension.

Extension page on mediawiki.org: https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Ask
Latest version of the install file: https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/r/gitweb?p=mediawiki/extensions/Ask.git;a=blob;f=INSTALL


== Requirements ==

Ask requires:

* PHP 5.3 or above
* If used as MediaWiki extension: MediaWiki 1.16 or later
** PHPUnit tests can require the latest MediaWiki

== Download ==

git clone https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/r/p/mediawiki/extensions/Ask.git

== Installation as MediaWiki extension ==

Once you have downloaded the code, place the ''Ask'' directory within your MediaWiki
'extensions' directory. Then add the following code to your [[Manual:LocalSettings.php|LocalSettings.php]] file:

# Diff
require_once( "$IP/extensions/Ask/Ask.php" );

== Installation as standalone library ==

